               <code codeSystem="2.16.840.1.113883.6.1" code="34069-5" displayName="HOW SUPPLIED SECTION"/>
               <title>HOW SUPPLIED</title>
               <text>
                  <paragraph>3.5g STERILE ointment supplied in an aluminum tube with a white polyethylene tip and white polyethylene cap (<content styleCode="bold">NDC </content>0065-0644-35), containing tobramycin 0.3% (3 mg/g).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
                     <content styleCode="bold">Storage: </content>Store at 8° - 27°C (46°- 80°F).</paragraph>
                  <paragraph>
